        "action": "Public inquiry into sentencing for child sexual offences",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The British public are sick of seeing child sexual offenders let off with community pay back orders or fines. The Government should launch a public inquiry to investigate sentencing for child sexual offences, and whether these are proportionate and protect the public from future offences.",
